127
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:31,710
What is this?

128
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,430
A big pancake.

129
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,960
On my way here,

130
00:07:34,990 --> 00:07:36,250
I passed by a breakfast stall.

131
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,920
But it was the only one which was open there.

132
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:39,700
I didn't want to make you feel neglected,

133
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:41,600
