151
00:08:12,570 --> 00:08:13,720
We can't be so picky about the food.

152
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:16,130
You're quite adaptive.

153
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:17,670
I have no choice.

154
00:08:18,790 --> 00:08:21,670
When I was a kid, my mom didn't allow me to eat the snacks bought from street stalls.

155
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:24,070
But now I think it tastes better than before.

156
00:08:24,150 --> 00:08:25,470
What's the problem with street stalls?

157
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,910
When I was a kid, I followed my grandpa to run a street stall.

158
00:08:27,910 --> 00:08:29,910
That's how Meton Popcorn was founded at first.

159
00:08:30,230 --> 00:08:30,790
Really?

160
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,409
Grandpa Zhong is amazing.

161
00:08:34,309 --> 00:08:35,159
